title: LF B1+ Duo Partner to move into Silver with - Must be Dedicated
body:
Clawed my way back to Bronze 1 but cant get out due to provisional players
with no idea thus turning toxic.

So Im looking for a duo partner to move out of Bronze with and continue through
silver.

Add me in game "Chocco", Im a QLD player and Im usually on after 4pm every day for a few hours

My lanes are: 
Top - {{champion:74}} Heimer,{{champion:17}}  Teemo, {{champion:75}} Nasus, {{champion:23}} Tryn
Mid - {{champion:74}} Heimer
Sup - {{champion:37}} Sona,{{champion:53}}  Blitz, {{champion:111}} Naut
JG - {{champion:427}} Ivern
